  "title": "Technician (Lab Testing) #79905",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Testing & Measurements</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ayer Rajah (Near MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Mon – Thu (8.30AM - 6PM); Fri (8.30AM - 5.30PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with the daily functioning of the product testing lab.</li><li>Perform product testing for customers based on established testing methods and standards.</li><li>Assist with routine maintenance and minor servicing of laboratory equipment.</li><li>Adhere to safety guidelines and maintain cleanliness within the laboratory.</li><li>Handle the receiving, organizing, and issuing of spare parts.</li><li>Pack and prepare parts for shipment, ensuring secure and accurate delivery.</li><li>Liaise with the logistics team to carry out dispatch tasks aligned with operational needs.</li><li>Handle and store parts properly to minimize damage or loss.</li><li>Support quarterly and annual inventory checks and maintain up-to-date records of all spare parts.</li><li>Ensure office storerooms are kept clean and organised.</li><li>Help with general office upkeep, including light replacements and minor electrical or facility- related repairs.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Nitec/ Higher Nitec in Electrical/ Mechanical Engineering or equivalent.</li><li>At least 1-2 years of related experience.</li><li>Competent in using Microsoft Office tools.</li><li>Familiarity with electrical systems is an added advantage.</li><li>Practical experience in packing, labelling, and coordinating both domestic and international shipments.</li><li>Capable of working independently and as part of a team.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79905 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
